
license: OFL
category: sans-serif
subsets: menu,latin,latin-ext

family: Quattrocento Sans

designer: Pablo Impallari

approved: true
description: <p>Quattrocento Sans is a classic, elegant \
  and sober typeface family. Warm, readable and not \
  intrusive. It's the perfect sans-serif companion \
  for Quattrocento.</p> \
  <p>The wide and open letterforms and large x-height \
  make it very legible for body text at small sizes. \
  All the tiny details that only shows up at bigger \
  sizes make it also great for display use.</p> \
  <p>Join the project at \
  <a href="http://www.impallari.com/projects/overview/quattrocento-sans-family">www.impallari.com/projects</a></p>

font.QuattrocentoSans-Regular.ttf.style: normal
font.QuattrocentoSans-Bold.ttf.style: normal
font.QuattrocentoSans-Italic.ttf.style: italic
font.QuattrocentoSans-BoldItalic.ttf.style: italic

font.QuattrocentoSans-Regular.ttf.weight: 400
font.QuattrocentoSans-Bold.ttf.weight: 700
font.QuattrocentoSans-Italic.ttf.weight: 400
font.QuattrocentoSans-BoldItalic.ttf.weight: 700

